# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:17
translate chinese welchs5_5512a7c3:

    # sst "Oh, that would be Flora."
    sst "哦，那是弗洛拉。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:18
translate chinese welchs5_5297860c:

    # sst "She's been my best friend literally since we were kids."
    sst "她从我们还是孩子起就一直是我最好的朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:19
translate chinese welchs5_5190cec5:

    # sst "We were friends all through high school and then we went to the same college too."
    sst "整个高中时期我们都是朋友，后来我们还上了同一所大学。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:20
translate chinese welchs5_33ec11b4:

    # sst "Then, when I got married and moved here to Skyhill, she followed me and moved here a few months later. "
    sst "后来，我结婚搬到了斯凯希尔，她几个月后也跟着我搬了过来。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:21
translate chinese welchs5_ca813fad:

    # pc "Is she the one who is always giving me dirty looks?"
    pc "就是那个总是用嫌弃眼神看我的人吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:23
translate chinese welchs5_15474dcf:

    # sst "Hah, probably. That sounds like her."
    sst "哈，大概吧。听起来很像她。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:24
translate chinese welchs5_94c344cc:

    # sst "She's pretty protective of me. And a little jealous too."
    sst "她对我挺保护的。还有点嫉妒。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:26
translate chinese welchs5_259e5b51:

    # sst "She's in love with me."
    sst "她爱我。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:27
translate chinese welchs5_e89e0515:

    # pc "Oh really?"
    pc "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:28
translate chinese welchs5_f7b116b6:

    # sst "Yeah."
    sst "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:30
translate chinese welchs5_d1cd9473:

    # sst "I've tried to get her to go out with other women, but she hasn't had any real relationship."
    sst "我试着让她和其他女人约会，但她一直没谈过什么像样的恋爱。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:31
translate chinese welchs5_c613154a:

    # sst "She keeps coming back to me."
    sst "她总是回到我身边。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:32
translate chinese welchs5_3fe761a2:

    # pc "But you're not in love with her?"
    pc "但你并不爱她？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:34
translate chinese welchs5_ab2bde78:

    # sst "No."
    sst "不。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:35
translate chinese welchs5_5efe064d:

    # sst "I love her, but not like that."
    sst "我爱她，但不是那种爱。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:37
translate chinese welchs5_9a8d8452:

    # sst "What can I say? I like dick too much."
    sst "我还能说什么呢？我太喜欢男人的鸡巴了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:38
translate chinese welchs5_2b34459b:

    # sst "I've had sex with women. I've had sex with Flora even. But I much prefer guys."
    sst "我和女人上过床。甚至和弗洛拉也上过。但我更喜欢男人。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:40
translate chinese welchs5_cb65f758:

    # sst "But we're very good friends. I care about her a lot."
    sst "不过我们是特别好的朋友。我很在乎她。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:41
translate chinese welchs5_06a47599:

    # pc "Do you think it's a little weird that you are just friends with her, but she's in love with you?"
    pc "你不觉得有点奇怪吗？你只把她当朋友，她却爱着你？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:42
translate chinese welchs5_e5498a93:

    # pc "Like it seems a little unhealthy."
    pc "感觉有点不健康。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:43
translate chinese welchs5_0b692e30:

    # sst "I don't think so."
    sst "我不这么觉得。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:44
translate chinese welchs5_2e65f684:

    # sst "We've talked a lot about it. About how I don't want a romantic relationship with her. How I want to be with a man."
    sst "我们聊过很多次了。聊过我不想要和她谈恋爱，聊过我想和男人在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:46
translate chinese welchs5_039529b3:

    # sst "But relationships are messy, you know?"
    sst "但感情关系很复杂，你知道的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:48
translate chinese welchs5_221cdb4c:

    # sst "We love each other. We are very close. But that's it."
    sst "我们彼此深爱，关系非常亲密。但仅此而已。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:50
translate chinese welchs5_691f6a18:

    # sst "I don't get fuzzy feelings in my chest when I'm around her, like I do when I'm around you."
    sst "和她在一起时，我心里不会像和你在一起时那样怦然心动。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:52
translate chinese welchs5_154a26fd:

    # sst "Hopefully some day she will find somebody who gives her those feelings too."
    sst "希望有一天她也能遇到一个能让她产生这种感觉的人。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs5.rpy:53
translate chinese welchs5_620e83da:

    # sst "And I'll just keep on being her friend and loving her."
    sst "而我，会一直做她的朋友，一直爱着她。"

